snippet.title: ATHENS 2047 | Early Alpha Footage | Phobos Subhuman
snippet.description:
Phobos (Subhuman) is the first part of a two-game series. The plot is based on current sociopolitical standards combined with ancient astronomical indisputable clues. It constructs a fictional and at the same time strangely familiar world for the player to experience.
